WEBVTT

00:07:27.613 --> 00:07:31.553
No one had ever focused on pain
this way before.

00:07:32.928 --> 00:07:34.928
After that, he hit the books.

00:07:35.845 --> 00:07:38.708
He read every medical textbook
he could get his hands on,

00:07:38.732 --> 00:07:41.283
carefully noting every mention
of the word "pain."

00:07:42.282 --> 00:07:46.163
Out of the 14,000 pages he read,

00:07:46.187 --> 00:07:50.363
the word "pain" was
on 17 and a half of them.

00:07:50.908 --> 00:07:52.910
Seventeen and a half.

00:07:52.934 --> 00:07:58.206
For the most basic, most common,
most frustrating part of being a patient.

00:07:58.875 --> 00:08:00.982
Bonica was shocked -- I'm quoting him,